---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base
  title="Contact GAVI AFRICA LIMITED — Auto Service in Abule-Egba, Lagos"
  description="Call, WhatsApp, email, or walk in. GAVI AFRICA Auto Experience Centre: 3, Abiodun Onitiri Avenue, Awori Bus-Stop, Abule-Egba, Lagos. +234 705 300 9305."
  activePage="contact"
>
<!-- ============ PAGE HERO ============ -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span class="crumb-sep">/</span>Contact
    </nav>
    <span class="eyebrow">GET IN TOUCH</span>
    <h1>One number. One address. One advisor who picks up.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Call, WhatsApp, email, or walk in. The service advisor is at the desk Mon to Fri 8am to 5pm, and Saturday 8am to 2pm. If you have an urgent need outside those hours, send us a WhatsApp message and we will get back as soon as possible.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ CONTACT CHANNELS ============ -->
<section class="channels">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="channels-grid">

      <div class="channel">
        <div class="channel-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 01-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 014.11 2h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.13.96.37 1.9.72 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.91.35 1.85.59 2.81.72A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="channel-label">CALL US</div>
        <h3>Service Advisor</h3>
        <div class="channel-value">+234 705 300 9305</div>
        <p>Mon to Fri 8 AM to 5 PM. Saturday 8 AM to 2 PM. Takes calls, SMS, and WhatsApp on the same number.</p>
        <a href="tel:+2347053009305" class="btn btn-primary channel-btn">Call now →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="channel">
        <div class="channel-icon whatsapp" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M.057 24l1.687-6.163a11.867 11.867 0 0 1-1.587-5.945C.16 5.335 5.495 0 12.05 0a11.817 11.817 0 0 1 8.413 3.488 11.824 11.824 0 0 1 3.48 8.414c-.003 6.557-5.338 11.892-11.893 11.892a11.9 11.9 0 0 1-5.688-1.448L.057 24zm6.597-3.807c1.676.995 3.276 1.591 5.392 1.592 5.448 0 9.886-4.434 9.889-9.885.002-5.462-4.415-9.89-9.881-9.892-5.452 0-9.887 4.434-9.889 9.884-.001 2.225.651 3.891 1.746 5.634l-.999 3.648 3.742-.981zm11.387-5.464c-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347-.297-.149-1.758-.868-2.031-.967-.272-.099-.47-.149-.669.149-.198.297-.768.967-.941 1.165-.173.198-.347.223-.644.074-.297-.149-1.255-.462-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.297-.347.446-.521.151-.172.2-.296.3-.495.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51l-.57-.01c-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.095 3.2 5.076 4.487.709.306 1.263.489 1.694.626.712.226 1.36.194 1.872.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="channel-label">CHAT WITH US</div>
        <h3>WhatsApp Business</h3>
        <div class="channel-value">+234 807 900 0009</div>
        <p>Quickest way for a quote on a service, a part, or a vehicle enquiry. Photos and videos help us diagnose remotely.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/2348079000009" class="btn btn-primary channel-btn" style="background: var(--whatsapp);">WhatsApp us →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="channel">
        <div class="channel-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="channel-label">EMAIL US</div>
        <h3>General &amp; Support</h3>
        <div class="channel-value">support@gaviafrica.com</div>
        <p>Best for invoices, fleet enquiries, partnership conversations, and anything that needs a paper trail.</p>
        <a href="mailto:support@gaviafrica.com" class="btn btn-primary channel-btn">Send an email →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ CONTACT FORM ============ -->
<section class="contact-form-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-form-grid">

      <div class="contact-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">SEND A MESSAGE</span>
        <h2>Or write to us right here.</h2>
        <p>The form below routes to the right person on our side: service, sales, parts, or fleet. We respond within the hour during work time and first thing the next morning otherwise.</p>
        <div class="hours">
          <strong>Mon to Fri:</strong> 8:00 AM to 5:00 PM<br>
          <strong>Saturday:</strong> 8:00 AM to 2:00 PM<br>
          <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed<br>
          <em>Early Bird drop-off from 6:30 AM by booking. T&amp;Cs apply.</em>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form-box" id="contact-form" aria-label="Contact form">
        <div class="field">
          <label>What is this about? *</label>
          <div class="radio-tile-group">
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="topic" value="service" checked> Service / repair</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="topic" value="vehicle"> Buying a vehicle</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="topic" value="parts"> Spare parts</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="topic" value="fleet"> Fleet / corporate</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="topic" value="partnership"> Partnership</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="topic" value="other"> Something else</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cf-first">First name *</label>
            <input id="cf-first" name="first" type="text" required>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cf-last">Last name *</label>
            <input id="cf-last" name="last" type="text" required>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cf-phone">Phone *</label>
            <input id="cf-phone" name="phone" type="tel" placeholder="+234..." required>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cf-email">Email *</label>
            <input id="cf-email" name="email" type="email" required>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="cf-company">Company <span class="hint">(if fleet or partnership)</span></label>
          <input id="cf-company" name="company" type="text">
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="cf-message">Your message *</label>
          <textarea id="cf-message" name="message" placeholder="Vehicle make and model if relevant, what you need, when you need it..." required></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label>Preferred reply channel</label>
          <div class="radio-tile-group">
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="reply" value="call" checked> Call me back</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="reply" value="whatsapp"> WhatsApp</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="reply" value="email"> Email</label>
            <label class="radio-tile"><input type="radio" name="reply" value="any"> Any of these</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; padding: 18px;">Send message →</button>
      </form>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ LOCATION / MAP ============ -->
<section class="location-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="location-grid">

      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">FIND THE CENTRE</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">3, Abiodun Onitiri Avenue.</h2>
        <p class="location-address">
          3, Abiodun Onitiri Avenue,<br>
          Awori Bus-Stop, Abule-Egba,<br>
          Lagos, Nigeria
        </p>
        <ul class="location-landmarks">
          <li>2 minutes off the Abule-Egba expressway</li>
          <li>Right after the Awori bus stop, heading north</li>
          <li>Easy on-street parking; secure compound parking inside</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="location-actions">
          <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/vGPRSB1B4hJGyYT18" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Open in Google Maps →</a>
          <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?ll=6.6209108,3.3010742&q=GAVI+AFRICA" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">Open in Apple Maps →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Real Google Maps embed with directions overlay -->
      <div class="map-frame">
        <a
          href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/vGPRSB1B4hJGyYT18"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="map-directions-overlay"
          aria-label="Open GAVI AFRICA location in Google Maps for directions"
        >
          <span class="map-directions-btn">Get directions →</span>
        </a>
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=6.6209108,3.3010742&hl=en&z=16&output=embed"
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          style="border:0;"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="GAVI AFRICA Auto Experience Centre location"
        ></iframe>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FLEET INQUIRY ============ -->
<section class="fleet-inquiry">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow on-dark">FLEET DESK</span>
    <h2>Running 3 or more vehicles for your business?</h2>
    <p>The fleet desk handles scheduled service contracts, mobile-workshop visits, and one monthly bill for everything. Average response time on a fleet enquiry is under 2 hours during work time.</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a href="mailto:support@gaviafrica.com?subject=Fleet%20enquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Email the fleet desk →</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/2348079000009" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:#fff;border-color:#fff;">WhatsApp us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>

<script>
  // Contact form → Google Sheets via Apps Script web app.
  // Paste your deployed Apps Script /exec URL below (contact script, not the booking one).
  const CONTACT_ENDPOINT = 'PASTE_YOUR_CONTACT_APPS_SCRIPT_URL_HERE'

  const contactForm = document.getElementById('contact-form')
  if (contactForm) {
      contactForm.addEventListener('invalid', () => contactForm.classList.add('show-errors'), true)
    contactForm.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault()
      const btn = contactForm.querySelector('button[type="submit"]')
      const original = btn.textContent
      btn.textContent = 'Sending…'
      btn.disabled = true
      try {
        const data = Object.fromEntries(new FormData(contactForm).entries())
        data.submittedAt = new Date().toISOString()
        data.page = location.pathname
        await fetch(CONTACT_ENDPOINT, {
          method: 'POST',
          mode: 'no-cors',
          headers: {'Content-Type': 'text/plain;charset=utf-8'},
          body: JSON.stringify(data),
        })
        btn.textContent = 'Message sent ✓'
        contactForm.reset()
        setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = original; btn.disabled = false }, 4000)
      } catch (err) {
        btn.textContent = 'Something went wrong — call us instead'
        setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = original; btn.disabled = false }, 4000)
      }
    })
  }
</script>

<style>
/* Contact page */
  .channels { background: var(--paper); }
  .channels-grid {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-5);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  @media (min-width: 540px)  { .channels-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .channels-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
  .channel {
    background: var(--paper); border: 1.5px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: var(--s-8);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .channel:hover {
    border-color: var(--gavi-blue); transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(15, 26, 43, 0.06);
  }
  .channel-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 56px;
    background: var(--gavi-blue); color: #fff;
    -webkit-clip-path: polygon(50% 0, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0 75%, 0 25%);
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0 75%, 0 25%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-5);
  }
  .channel-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
  .channel-icon.whatsapp { background: var(--whatsapp); }
  .channel-label {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gavi-blue);
    letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-2);
  }
  .channel h3 { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: var(--s-3); }
  .channel .channel-value {
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--s-3); word-break: break-word;
  }
  .channel p {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-mute);
    line-height: 1.5; flex-grow: 1; margin-bottom: var(--s-5);
  }
  .channel .channel-btn {
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  /* Contact form */
  .contact-form-section {
    background: var(--paper-soft);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .contact-form-section::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; right: -10%;
    width: 50%; height: 100%;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 60 70'><polygon points='30,0 60,17.5 60,52.5 30,70 0,52.5 0,17.5' fill='none' stroke='%23246EB6' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.4'/></svg>");
    background-size: 80px 92px; opacity: 0.08; pointer-events: none;
  }
  .contact-form-section > .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .contact-form-grid {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-10);
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .contact-form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; gap: var(--s-16); } }
  .contact-copy h2 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .contact-copy h2 { font-size: 40px; } }
  .contact-copy p {
    font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin-bottom: var(--s-6); line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .contact-copy .hours {
    background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gavi-blue);
    padding: var(--s-5); border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .contact-copy .hours strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .contact-form-box {
    background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: var(--s-6);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(15, 26, 43, 0.04);
  }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .contact-form-box { padding: var(--s-10); } }
  .radio-tile-group {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-2);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  @media (min-width: 540px) { .radio-tile-group { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  .radio-tile {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--s-3);
    padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-4);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.15s ease; min-height: 48px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .radio-tile:hover { border-color: var(--gavi-blue); }
  .radio-tile input { width: 18px; height: 18px; accent-color: var(--gavi-blue); }

  /* Location section */
  .location-section { background: var(--paper); }
  .location-grid {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-10);
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .location-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; gap: var(--s-12); align-items: center; } }
  .location-address {
    font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--s-5);
  }
  .location-landmarks {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-mute);
    line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--s-6);
  }
  .location-landmarks li {
    padding-left: var(--s-5); position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-2); list-style: none;
  }
  .location-landmarks li::before {
    content: '↳'; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0;
    color: var(--gavi-blue); font-weight: 700;
  }
  .location-actions { display: flex; gap: var(--s-3); flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .map-frame {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 26, 43, 0.12);
  }
  .map-frame iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; border: 0; }
  .map-directions-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--s-4);
    right: var(--s-4);
    z-index: 2;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .map-directions-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--gavi-blue);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(36, 110, 182, 0.35);
    transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }
  .map-directions-btn:hover {
    background: var(--gavi-blue-dark);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* Fleet inquiry callout */
  .fleet-inquiry {
    background: var(--ink); color: #D8E0EC;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .fleet-inquiry h2 { color: #fff; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .fleet-inquiry h2 { font-size: 40px; } }
  .fleet-inquiry p { color: #B8C5D6; font-size: 17px; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto var(--s-6); }
  .fleet-inquiry .actions { display: flex; gap: var(--s-3); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* Highlight missing required fields after a failed submit attempt */
  :global(form.show-errors input:invalid),
  :global(form.show-errors select:invalid),
  :global(form.show-errors textarea:invalid) {
    border-color: #D63031 !important;
    background: #FFF5F5;
  }
</style>
